description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 6, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 6, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Nine Lives for East, Box for South, and 5 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30061-79451-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [6 Votes, Common]
